Ivy A Thomson and William A Thomson Graduate Scholarship -15000
Eligibility:
Year(s) of Eligibility:Nominee is registered in, or admitted to, a master's or doctoral degree program at the UofA

Academic Requirements: Superior Academic Achievement 

Must be engaged in Full Time Time study

Program of Study: Nominee must be registered and working full-time on their graduate program during the tenure of the scholarship
